media:group.media:title: burgerpunk2077
media:group.media:description:
The age is 2077.Food animals and plants were extinct and people were hungry.
Politics is corrupt and only one large corporate group effectively dominates the world.
People were armed with the latest technology and aimed at the food stored by the megacorporation.

The first half is stop motion animation. In the second half, I'm shooting a video.
This is not a promotional video for McDonald's and Cyberpunk 2077.
